summary: WINDOW REGULATOR IN PASSENGER SIDE WINDOW WENT OUT. THIS IS THE 2ND TIME THIS HAS HAPPENED TO MY JEEP GRAND CHEROKEE. IT IS A 2002. THE FIRST WAS ABOUT 2 MONTHS AGO WHEN THIS PROBLEM HAPPENED WITH THE DRIVER SIDE WINDOW. THESE HAVE EACH COST ME 300 DOLLARS. THE PART IS FAULTY AND JEEP OWNERS SHOULD BE COMPENSATED FOR HAVING TO PAY FOR POOR CRAFTSMANSHIP ON THE PART OF JEEP.
